                     <p>
                        <placeName key="place_109435">Oxford, St. Mildred’s</placeName>
                        <persName><forename>Roger</forename> <surname>Pilet</surname></persName> grants to <persName nymRef="Kepeharm"><forename>Petronilla</forename>, widow of <persName><forename>Hugh</forename> <surname>Kepeharm</surname></persName></persName>, the house [mentioned in W<supplied>igram</supplied> 618 <supplied>see MS. D. D. Ch. Ch. F. 110</supplied>]. 
